<subSubSection id="35C76538FF98FF80FDBBFE58639CEBCA" lastPageId="6" lastPageNumber="331" pageId="5" pageNumber="330" type="description">
<paragraph id="7D6236B3FF98FF83FDBBFE58638EEBDC" blockId="5.[496,836,433,506]" box="[619,737,479,504]" pageId="5" pageNumber="330">
(
<figureCitation id="E5E62A36FF98FF83FDA3FE5863B6EBDC" box="[627,729,479,504]" captionStart="Leptocysta" captionStartId="5.[381,471,1542,1558]" captionTargetBox="[253,1115,736,1520]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="Leptocysta tertia n. sp. — Fig. 5: Desenho total; fig. 6: perfil." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3417944" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3417944/files/figure.png" pageId="5" pageNumber="330">Figs. 5-6</figureCitation>
)
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="7D6236B3FF98FF83FF3DFD966392E8F3" pageId="5" pageNumber="330">
Cabeça escura com cinco espinhos curtos 
<emphasis id="4FA9EAA1FF98FF83FCCCFD966248E80E" box="[796,807,529,554]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="330">e</emphasis>
amarelados, todos mais ou menos do mesmo tamanho e dirigidos para frente. Búcula alta e castanha. Rostro castanho 
<emphasis id="4FA9EAA1FF98FF83FE46FDD160B9E84B" box="[406,470,598,623]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="330">claro</emphasis>
. Abertura rostral muito estreita, alta e formada de largas aréolas. Antenas castanhas, o último segmento com 
<emphasis id="4FA9EAA1FF98FF83FC12FDFF62A1E8B5" box="[962,974,632,657]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="330">a</emphasis>
metade apical, escura; o primeiro segmento o dobro do segundo, o terceiro um pouco mais de duas vezes 
<emphasis id="4FA9EAA1FF98FF83FE96FD39603EE8F3" box="[326,337,702,727]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="330">e</emphasis>
meia o comprimento do quarto.
</paragraph>
<caption id="29A2663BFF98FF83FEADF98162B5EC32" ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3417944" ID-Zenodo-Dep="3417944" box="[381,986,1542,1558]" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3417944/files/figure.png" pageId="5" pageNumber="330" startId="5.[381,471,1542,1558]" subCaptionStartIDs="5.[640,669,1542,1558] 5.[861,886,1542,1558]" subCaptionStarts="Fig. 5 &amp; fig. 6" targetBox="[253,1115,736,1520]" targetPageId="5">
<paragraph id="7D6236B3FF98FF83FEADF98162B5EC32" blockId="5.[381,986,1541,1558]" box="[381,986,1542,1558]" pageId="5" pageNumber="330">
<taxonomicName id="BADD4D30FF98FF83FEADF981637DEC32" authority="Monte, 1946" authorityName="Monte" authorityYear="1946" box="[381,530,1542,1558]" class="Insecta" family="Tingidae" genus="Leptocysta" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="330" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="tertia" status="n. sp.">
Leptocysta 
<emphasis id="4FA9EAA1FF98FF83FE36F981637DEC32" box="[486,530,1542,1558]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="330">tertia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="549A57DAFF98FF83FDF0F9816339EC32" box="[544,598,1542,1558]" pageId="5" pageNumber="330" rank="species">n. sp.</taxonomicNameLabel>
— Fig. 5: Desenho total; fig. 6: perfil.
</paragraph>
</caption>
<paragraph id="7D6236B3FF98FF83FF24F9C765F3ECBA" blockId="5.[190,1182,1599,1867]" pageId="5" pageNumber="330">
Pronoto pouco elevado, castanho, ligeiramente pontuado, trazendo pêlos dourados. Paranotos largos, altos, dirigidos para cima, sinuosos, quase totalmente manchados de escuro, com espinhos fortes e 
<emphasis id="4FA9EAA1FF98FF83FCEAF90262E2ECBA" box="[826,909,1669,1694]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="330">aguclos</emphasis>
em todas 
<emphasis id="4FA9EAA1FF98FF83FBC2F9036547ECB9" box="[1042,1064,1668,1693]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="330">as</emphasis>
margens.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="7D6236B3FF98FF83FF25F9216050ECC0" blockId="5.[190,1182,1599,1867]" pageId="5" pageNumber="330">
<emphasis id="4FA9EAA1FF98FF83FF25F9216035EC9B" box="[245,346,1702,1727]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="330">Vesícula</emphasis>
grande, curvada, manchada de escuro, e se alongando muito além da 
<emphasis id="4FA9EAA1FF98FF83FF38F94C6053ECC0" box="[232,316,1739,1764]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="330">cabeça</emphasis>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="7D6236B3FF98FF83FF27F96D6201ED6D" blockId="5.[190,1182,1599,1867]" pageId="5" pageNumber="330">
Carena mediana tão alta quanto a vesícula, porém 
<emphasis id="4FA9EAA1FF98FF83FC40F96D62A1ED27" box="[912,974,1770,1795]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="330">curta</emphasis>
e manchada de preto na parte posterior, e uma leve mancha da mesma 
<emphasis id="4FA9EAA1FF98FF83FC5BF88B62DFED01" box="[907,944,1804,1829]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="330">cor</emphasis>
na parte anterior; carenas laterais distintas, uniareoladas e não paralelas.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="7D6236B3FF9BFF80FF09FE9A63B4EBE2" blockId="6.[162,1159,284,949]" pageId="6" pageNumber="331">
Élitros largos, estreitados na frente e atrás, e nesta 
<emphasis id="4FA9EAA1FF9BFF80FCB8FE9A62C8EB12" box="[872,935,285,310]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="331">parte</emphasis>
levemente levantado, 
<emphasis id="4FA9EAA1FF9BFF80FF3DFEC6606BEB7E" box="[237,260,321,346]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="331">as</emphasis>
margens com uma série de espinhos em todo o seu contorno. Área costal bi, tri e 
<emphasis id="4FA9EAA1FF9BFF80FE87FEE16367EB5B" box="[343,520,358,383]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="331">quadrisseriada</emphasis>
, com duas largas manchas 
<emphasis id="4FA9EAA1FF9BFF80FC8BFEE162DEEB5B" box="[859,945,358,383]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="331">escuras</emphasis>
, uma na metade anterior e 
<emphasis id="4FA9EAA1FF9BFF80FEE3FE0E602FEB86" box="[307,320,393,418]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="331">a</emphasis>
outra na parte apical; subcostal bisseriada; discoidal excavada, escura, manchada de aréolas esbranquiçadas.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="7D6236B3FF9BFF80FF0BFE53639CEBCA" blockId="6.[162,1159,284,949]" box="[219,755,468,494]" pageId="6" pageNumber="331">
Comprimento 
<quantity id="BA259B56FF9BFF80FE42FE52636CEBCA" box="[402,515,469,494]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.47" pageId="6" pageNumber="331" unit="mm" value="3.47">3.47 mm</quantity>
.; largura 
<quantity id="BA259B56FF9BFF80FD52FE526380EBCA" box="[642,751,469,494]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.26" pageId="6" pageNumber="331" unit="mm" value="2.26">2.26 mm</quantity>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
